Adult‑Clean Version
Flow is the continuous upward movement from Center to Apex. It does not begin or end; only awareness of it changes. Meditation, group resonance, and near‑death experiences expand human perception of this flow. These experiences do not create flow — they reveal it.
ProjectCompass provides a structure for re-entering flow through directional alignment and geometric awareness.









